            ],
            [
              "Claire"
            ]
          ],
          "note": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "string": "Alternative easy team similar to Solo Ember, though it scores less points than the other 2 teams."
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "string": "{P/Mero}: min {S/SPD}, T4 {I-W/Heartunder's Blade}, T4 {AS/Revenge}, 268+ {S/EFF} (otherwise turn on the +150 {S/EFF} geas). Turn on the resilience +50/200 geas if you can reach enough {S/EFF} for those too."
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "string": "{P/Claire}: T4 {I-A/Resurrection Token}, 6* transcendence, {I-T/Vanguard's Charm} and 2 {AS/Bursting} to burst 2 on her first turn. Must be slower than {P/Mero}. 6* transcendence, {I-T/Vanguard's Charm} +10 and EE+5 should also be enough AP without a burst set."
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "string": "The other 2 teammates should just be talisman holders that die before they can move. {C/Defender}s can hold {I-A/Charmer's Golden Chalice} to die easier if necessary."
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "string": "{P/Mero} should start with S3 then spam S2 whenever possible (don't use burst 2+). If you can't S2, switch to S3 then back to S2."
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "string": "If you overkill the boss, you can turn off the {E/Fire} ATK+ geas for more points."
            }
          ]
        }
      }
